

# Conventional Commits:
# Structure: `type[(scope)][!]: commit title`
#
# Types: 
#  - feat: Feature Introduction (SemVer MINOR)
#  - fix: Bugfix (SemVer PATCH)
#  - chore: Recurring Changes, e.g. updating of dependencies
#  - ci: Pipeline changes
#  - docs: Documentation changes
#  - refactor: Code refactoring
# `!` indicates breaking changes (SemVer MAJOR)
